After the following code runs, what will be the value of `result`?

```js
var x = 10;

function foo (y) {
  y = 20;
}

foo(x);
var result = x;
```

After the following code runs, what will be the value of `result`?

```js
var x = 10;

function f (y) {
  y += 20;
}

f(x);
var result = x;
```

